caption.text: Sarku Japan in Niles, Illinois: If you like teppanyaki style cooking just like Benihana, then I suggest trying Sarku! The closest location to my home is in the Golf Mill Mall. They have a variety of meals to choose from as well as sushi ^ - ^ My family & I normally order the chicken teriyaki dinner. It's about $5.49 & it's pretty filling. I think they do a good job with the portion size. When you order this, they'll ask you if you want fried or white rice. I got fried rice. The fried rice is on the bottom, then veggies on top, & topped with the teriyaki chicken! It's very delicious & worth it! The Asian in me was very happy 😜 いただきます。😋🎎
